FBIS3-18881 "drweu046_q_94006" FBIS-WEU-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 TURKEY Former DEP Chief Allegedly Escapes Abroad NC0803191894 London Kanal-6 Television in Turkish 1700 GMT 8 Mar 94 NC0803191894 London Kanal-6 Television Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Text] Claims that Yasar Kaya, former leader of Democracy Party [DEP] and owner of OZGUR GUNDEM, has escaped abroad are gaining acceptance. It is being reported that Kaya is already in Germany and will ask for political asylum there. In the meantime, Istanbul State Security Court ordered Kaya's detention in absentia. Kaya is being tried on charges of engaging in separatist propaganda in his articles in OZGUR GUNDEM. OZGUR GUNDEM officials say that Kaya has not contacted them at all.
